---
title: Lemon-Pepper Chicken & Capsicum Mayo with Garlicky Roast Potato Toss & Chilli Flakes
description: Turn up the flavour with tonight’s tantalising pork dish, served with a smokey chargrilled capsicum mayo that brings a burst of sunny zest to every bite. Paired with garlicky roasted potatoes for a hearty twist and a sprinkle of chilli flakes for just the right kick, this dish is a fun, bold blend of spice, crunch, and creamy goodness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
